definitions.definition: A village on the River Shannon , County Leitrim , Ireland .
A village north-west of Castlewellan , County Down , Northern Ireland ( Irish grid ref J3039 ) .
A neighbourhood of Gloucester , Ottawa , Ontario , Canada .
